{"tid":1077213,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A] 小弟寫左隻簡單既Android game","createTime":"2019-03-25T12:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T08:57:58.000Z","uid":244648,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"999f91c416681e45235a6dd949769e63efc9141b","tid":1077213,"uid":244648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"1.隻GAME 叫Numbers<br />\n<br />\n2.隻game 玩咩?<br />\n玩法好簡單，用你最快既速度（最少既小間）順序禁哂所有數字<br />\n<br />\n3.每關有咩唔同?<br />\n第一關會有10個數字(1-10) ，每升一LV. 會多5個數字<br />\n<br />\n4. 點升LV.?<br />\nI. 2顆星星及冇按錯<br />\nII. 3顆星星<br />\n<br />\n5. 星星:<br />\n一星: 你有10s用於頭10個數字，其後每加一個數字加1.2s<br />\n二星: 你有10s用於頭10個數字，其後每加一個數字加1s<br />\n三星: 你有10s用於頭10個數字，其後每加一個數字加0.8s<br />\n例如，係第三關: 你會有14S (6s + 0.8s x10) 完成整個關卡及取得三星<br />\n<br />\n6.有冇廣告<br />\n有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/25/sZ7FM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F25%2FsZ7FM4.jpg&h=753d42d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/25/0POA6H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F25%2F0POA6H.jpg&h=b07926ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/25/OTyn0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F25%2FOTyn0i.jpg&h=16b47644&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDownload:<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=invencion.numbers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dinvencion.numbers&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7353b587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=invencion.numbers</a>"},{"pid":"f5c3603ea80f152ffeee7d1a235b95c89b4ce99d","tid":1077213,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93d79ad71fc38798